tary policy, and was the primary force in negotiating EMU.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / European.2bisacsh1 aHeisenberg, Dorothee, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertLynne Rienner Press Complete Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000z97831107842680 cprintz978155587689040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978168585181140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781685851811423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781685851811/original  a978-3-11-078426-8  Lynne Rienner Press Complete Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK